{"article_id":"BuQrgwemN8U7a3X1","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"They are special investigations into the backgrounds of nominees to the Supreme Court and other high profile jobs in any presidential administration .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"Perhaps never before has such attention been focused on the long-shrouded process than in the case of Brett Kavanaugh .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"And Friday brought a new and unexpected wrinkle :","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Republican senators and President Donald Trump acquiesced to Democrats ' demand for the re-opening of Kavanaugh ' s background inquiry","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"to vet allegations of sexual assault against the Supreme Court nominee","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"leveled by high school acquaintance Christine Blasey Ford .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"While an extraordinary Senate Judiciary Committee hearing did little","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"to reconcile the dueling accounts","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"offered by Ford and Kavanaugh ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"lawmakers now believe","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"that a clearer picture of the nominee ' s credibility would likely emerge","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"and Trump Friday authorized a `` limited '' one-week FBI review .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Only the White House was authorized to re-open the background review ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"closed","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"long before Ford ' s allegations were made public .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"But even in the narrow amount of time","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"provided by Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"former FBI officials said","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"agents could reach a quick resolution .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"\" They could knock this thing out in a couple of days , \"","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"said Jim Davis , a former agent","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"who participated in at least 50 such background inquiries .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"\" The great and beautiful thing about the FBI is that it can apply incredible resources to whatever the issue requires . \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Phil Mudd , a former CIA and FBI official","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"who has been the subject of a half-dozen background checks ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"such re-investigation is common","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and can be completed fairly quickly .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"`` You have to let things go","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"where they go ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"but","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"if it is narrow in scope","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"it could take just a few days , ''","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"Mudd said .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Apart from Ford , among the first witnesses","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"likely to be contacted by investigators","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"is Kavanaugh 's high school friend , Mark Judge ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"who","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Ford claims","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"was in the room","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"when she was assaulted at a house party in the Washington , D.C. suburbs in 1982 .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Ford told the Senate panel","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"while she was allegedly being assaulted by Kavanaugh ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"she made eye contact with Judge","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"who she had hoped","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"would come to her aid .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Democrats had unsuccessfully sought to have Judge testify at Thursday 's hearing .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Judge , in a statement Friday , said","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"he would `` cooperate with any law enforcement agency","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"that is assigned to confidentially investigate these allegations . ''","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Judge had previously told the committee in a sworn statement","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"that he had `` no memory '' of the incident","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"outlined by Ford .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"In her testimony , Ford identified two others","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"who were allegedly present at the party ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"P.J . Smyth and Leland Ingham Keyser .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Both of them also have issued statements","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"indicating","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"that they no recollection of the party .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Davis , the former FBI agent , said","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"all of those","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"identified as being present at the party","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"would almost certainly be interviewed , as well the people","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"who Ford told of the incident .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Prior to Thursday 's hearing , Ford 's attorneys provided the Senate committee with sworn declarations from four people ,","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"including Ford 's husband ,","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"who said","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"that Ford had shared details of the incident and Kavanaugh 's alleged involvement with them .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"Trump calls Ford 's testimony 'compelling ,","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"' orders new FBI probe of Kavanaugh","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"Kavanaugh confirmation :","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"Yale Law joins American Bar Association in request for FBI probe","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"More :","depth":4},{"id":76,"text":"What just happened ?","depth":4},{"id":77,"text":"Here 's a breakdown of the Brett Kavanaugh vote and what happens next","depth":4},{"id":78,"text":"Ford 's husband , Russell Ford , said","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"he first learned of his wife 's experience with sexual assault `` around the time","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"we got married . ''","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"However , he said","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"Ford did not share details of the incident until a couple 's therapy session in 2012 .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"`` I remember her saying","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"that her attacker 's name was Brett Kavanaugh ,","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"that he was a successful lawyer","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"who had grown up in Christine 's hometown ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"and that he was well known in the Washington , D.C. , community , ''","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Russell Ford said .","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"It was unclear whether the scope of an FBI inquiry would allow for the review of other allegations","depth":5},{"id":90,"text":"leveled by former Yale classmate , Deborah Ramirez ,","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"who claimed","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"that Kavanaugh exposed himself at a drunken party during the 1983-84 academic year .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"Another woman , Julie Swetnick , has alleged","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"that in the 1980s she witnessed Kavanaugh and Judge attempt to ply teenage girls with alcohol at wild parties","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"where girls were sexually abused .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"She did not say","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"Kavanaugh or Judge sexually assaulted her .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"In his statement Friday , Judge said","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"he did not recall attending the parties .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"`` The allegations in the Swetnick affidavit are so bizarre","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"that ,","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"even while suffering from my addiction ,","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"I would remember actions so outlandish .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"I categorically deny them , ''","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"`` The FBI is going to put together a list ,","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"and you can bet","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"that all of the people","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"whose names have been floated out there","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"are going to be on it , ''","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"said Ray Mey , a former FBI agent","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"who conducted dozens of background checks during his tenure at the bureau .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"`` The FBI has more than enough resources","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"to do this in a week , ''","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"`` What I worry about , is that nobody comes out of this looking good ,","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"including the FBI . ''","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"If the FBI discovers derogatory information ,","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"Mey said","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"the FBI risks invoking the wrath of the president","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"who has accused of the bureau of attempting to sabotage his administration as part of its inquiry into Russia 's interference in the 2016 election .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"`` If they do n't find anything ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"the other side will say","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"it 's a cover-up , ''","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"Mey said .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"`` Either way , the bureau does n't gain anything . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":253,"left":195,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":160,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":128,"right":159,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":159,"left":131,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":2,"right":130,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":130,"left":3,"right":129,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":139,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclea